description: Ink is an interface kit for quick development of web interfaces, simple to use and expand on. It uses a combination of HTML, CSS and JavaScript to offer modern solutions for building layouts, display common interface elements and implement interactive features that are content-centric and user friendly for both your audience and your designers & developers.
summary: An HTML5/CSS3 framework used at SAPO for fast and efficient website design and prototyping.
title: SAPO Ink
